1) file : memTransfer.cu pinMemTransfer.cu 
   compile : nvcc memTransfer.cu 
             nvcc pinMemTransfer.cu 
   run     : ./a.out

2) file : memTransferVariable.cu pinMemTransferVariable.cu
   compile : nvcc memTransferVariable.cu 
             nvcc pinMemTransferVariable.cu 
   run     : ./a.out memorysize(Mib) 
             ex) ./a.out 2 - set memorysize 2Mib 

3) file : globalVariable_2.cu 
   compile : nvcc globalVariable_2.cu 
   run     : ./a.out

4) file : readSegment.cu 
   compile : nvcc readSegment.cu 
   run     : ./a.out 


